tarts from the position of the subject. It also permits changing perspectives. This design concept should attract attention far beyond the borders of France.  aInnovative Krankenhaus-Architekturen  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aArchitectural firmszFrancexHistoryy21st century. 0aArchitecturezFrancey21st century. 4aHospital Design. 7aARCHITECTURE / Individual Architects & Firms / General.2bisacsh1 aAgence Brunet Saunier Architecture, , eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Architecture, Design and Arts 2000 - 2014z9783110635690oZDB-23-GAA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Art and Architecture 2000-2014 (EN)z978311062112908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2012z9783110288995oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE ARTS AND ARCHITECTURE 2012z978311031669808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET KUNST UND ARCHITEKTUR 2012z9783110317046oZDB-23-DKA0 cprintz978303460816940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978303461090240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783034610902423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783034610902/original  a978-3-11-023857-0  DGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1c2000d2014  a978-3-11-031669-8  E-BOOK PACKAGE ARTS AND ARCHITECTURE 2012b2012  a978-3-11-062112-9  DGBA Backlist Art and Architecture 2000-2014 (EN)c2000d2014  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_AD  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  a